				align-items: center;
				position: relative;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 50%, #312e81 100%);
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.hero::before {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				right: 0;
				bottom: 0;
				background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
